Model definition for Books.VolumeUserInfo. User specific information related to this volume. (e.g. page this user last read or whether they purchased this book) This class models an object which will be transmitted to or from the Lets you search for books and manage your Google Books library. service. To reduce the data transferred during service requests, you may remove members that contain data elements that your application does not need.
